1
00:00:10,805 --> 00:00:13,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like Uehara.</font>

2
00:00:21,039 --> 00:00:22,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

3
00:00:35,972 --> 00:00:38,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uhm...
-How's your fever?</font>

4
00:00:39,672 --> 00:00:42,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's OK now.
-Oh, I see.</font>

5
00:00:45,972 --> 00:00:47,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did he hear me?</font>

6
00:00:48,039 --> 00:00:50,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Or didn't he?</font>

7
00:00:51,105 --> 00:00:53,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Which is it?</font>

8
00:00:54,205 --> 00:00:57,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Argh!
-What? Did you say something?</font>

9
00:00:59,505 --> 00:01:01,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No... Nothing at all.</font>

10
00:01:07,105 --> 00:01:08,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He heard.</font>

11
00:01:09,305 --> 00:01:10,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He didn't hear.</font>

12
00:01:11,505 --> 00:01:12,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He heard.</font>

13
00:01:12,939 --> 00:01:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He didn't hear.</font>

14
00:01:16,605 --> 00:01:17,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

15
00:01:21,672 --> 00:01:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh. Yours is in the fridge.</font>

16
00:01:25,305 --> 00:01:28,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, thank you.</font>

17
00:01:30,772 --> 00:01:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">By the way,</font>

18
00:01:33,005 --> 00:01:35,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you didn't happen to hear</font>

19
00:01:35,305 --> 00:01:37,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">what I said in the park just now,
did you?</font>

20
00:01:37,939 --> 00:01:39,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

21
00:01:40,072 --> 00:01:42,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank goodness.</font>

22
00:01:42,705 --> 00:01:45,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I <i>did hear you say that you liked me,
or something like that.</i></font>

23
00:01:46,405 --> 00:01:47,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

24
00:01:49,839 --> 00:01:50,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh no!</font>

25
00:01:50,872 --> 00:01:53,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You're faking it, right?
-Huh?</font>

26
00:01:53,505 --> 00:01:55,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry. I know you're not serious.</font>

27
00:02:02,205 --> 00:02:03,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, that's right.</font>

28
00:02:03,505 --> 00:02:05,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He would never give up
unless you said that, right?</font>

29
00:02:06,039 --> 00:02:07,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, yes. That's right.</font>

30
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:10,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I heard he's called
the king of the love confession.</font>

31
00:02:10,405 --> 00:02:12,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He falls in love with anyone
and tells them he loves them.</font>

32
00:02:18,705 --> 00:02:21,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm happy for you.
-Huh?</font>

33
00:02:22,105 --> 00:02:24,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's nice that there's someone
that thinks you're attractive.</font>

34
00:02:28,305 --> 00:02:29,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

35
00:02:43,939 --> 00:02:46,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What're you so angry about?
I was complimenting you.</font>

36
00:02:47,305 --> 00:02:49,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's no compliment!</font>

37
00:02:50,705 --> 00:02:52,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not funny.</font>

38
00:02:52,072 --> 00:02:53,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? I'm not laughing at you.</font>

39
00:02:53,872 --> 00:02:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That Uehara can sure be stupid.</font>

40
00:02:57,939 --> 00:03:00,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I guess I'm glad about it.</font>

41
00:03:00,505 --> 00:03:04,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it kind of ticks me off
that he doesn't think anything of me.</font>

42
00:03:05,872 --> 00:03:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, you actually like Uehara,
don't you?</font>

43
00:03:13,505 --> 00:03:16,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can tell. There's no need to hide it.</font>

44
00:03:18,005 --> 00:03:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not trying to hide it.</font>

45
00:03:20,705 --> 00:03:23,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I realized it myself recently.</font>

46
00:03:24,872 --> 00:03:26,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Finally, you accepted it.</font>

47
00:03:27,105 --> 00:03:30,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like I figured.
I was in love with Uehara too.</font>

48
00:03:30,305 --> 00:03:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I know it was hard to tell me.</font>

49
00:03:32,572 --> 00:03:34,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Sorry.
-Now, you listen to me.</font>

50
00:03:34,705 --> 00:03:37,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're more important to me
than Uehara is.</font>

51
00:03:38,205 --> 00:03:40,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Keeping it secret
from me really made me sad.</font>

52
00:03:41,405 --> 00:03:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Marina.</font>

53
00:03:44,305 --> 00:03:48,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so happy that I finally get to talk
about love life with you.</font>

54
00:03:48,205 --> 00:03:50,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You look happy.</font>

55
00:03:50,972 --> 00:03:52,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What're you doing for New Year's?</font>

56
00:03:52,872 --> 00:03:56,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm planning to go to my parent's.
You're going back too, right?</font>

57
00:03:56,672 --> 00:03:57,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

58
00:03:58,772 --> 00:04:01,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My brother and Yuri are going to be
in Hawaii on New Year's.</font>

59
00:04:01,672 --> 00:04:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hawaii?
-They said it's their honeymoon.</font>

60
00:04:05,472 --> 00:04:07,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

61
00:04:08,605 --> 00:04:11,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Then that means you're...
-Working.</font>

62
00:04:11,605 --> 00:04:14,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hourly wages go up during New Year's.</font>

63
00:04:15,572 --> 00:04:17,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll probably get a New Year's bonus too.</font>

64
00:04:18,305 --> 00:04:21,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You're spending New Year's Eve here?
-I'll just come home and go to bed.</font>

65
00:04:25,605 --> 00:04:27,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

66
00:04:28,105 --> 00:04:30,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Make sure you do your New Year's cleaning
before you go home.</font>

67
00:04:30,405 --> 00:04:31,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will.</font>

68
00:04:33,105 --> 00:04:35,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just so expensive
to travel home during New Year's.</font>

69
00:04:36,205 --> 00:04:39,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I used way too much money
to move in here.</font>

70
00:04:40,039 --> 00:04:42,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Plus I've got remedial lessons.</font>

71
00:04:43,005 --> 00:04:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>But, at least you can come home
for New Year's Day and after.</i></font>

72
00:04:47,705 --> 00:04:52,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But, you see, they asked me to work then.</font>

73
00:04:52,705 --> 00:04:56,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And spring vacation isn't that long
after winter vacation.</font>

74
00:04:56,305 --> 00:04:57,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I guess so.</i></font>

75
00:04:57,805 --> 00:05:01,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Besides, it won't be easy
to get a plane ticket now.</i></font>

76
00:05:01,505 --> 00:05:04,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Plane tickets are really expensive
during New Year's.</font>

77
00:05:05,305 --> 00:05:06,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Oh, all right.</i></font>

78
00:05:07,039 --> 00:05:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'll send you some New Year's gift money.</i></font>

79
00:05:09,772 --> 00:05:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Mom. Bye.</font>

80
00:05:19,305 --> 00:05:23,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This means... New Year's Eve with Uehara.</font>

81
00:05:28,205 --> 00:05:31,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy New Year.
I wish you all the best this year.</font>

82
00:05:31,772 --> 00:05:32,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Me too.</font>

83
00:05:46,005 --> 00:05:48,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is going to be so nice.</font>

84
00:06:14,039 --> 00:06:16,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? We're closed on New Year's?</font>

85
00:06:16,805 --> 00:06:18,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">On New Year's Eve, most people eat soba.</font>

86
00:06:18,805 --> 00:06:21,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's the only time ramen shops
can take a nice break.</font>

87
00:06:21,105 --> 00:06:24,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Every year we're open till the 30th
and start again on the third.</font>

88
00:06:24,705 --> 00:06:28,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No work, huh?
-You're going home, aren't you?</font>

89
00:06:29,072 --> 00:06:30,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

90
00:06:31,505 --> 00:06:32,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yes.</font>

91
00:06:33,939 --> 00:06:34,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Welcome!
-Welcome!</font>

92
00:06:36,039 --> 00:06:36,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

93
00:06:37,039 --> 00:06:39,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Daichi, what brings you here?
-I'm hungry.</font>

94
00:06:39,305 --> 00:06:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Actually, I'm a fan of this ramen now.</font>

95
00:06:43,505 --> 00:06:45,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thanks for revisiting!
-Thanks for revisiting!</font>

96
00:06:45,872 --> 00:06:47,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here you go.
-Looks great.</font>

97
00:06:47,505 --> 00:06:49,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

98
00:06:51,872 --> 00:06:53,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">By the way, Nao--</font>

99
00:06:53,305 --> 00:06:54,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome!</font>

100
00:06:55,705 --> 00:06:58,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Abe.
-What are you doing here, Nao?</font>

101
00:06:58,972 --> 00:07:01,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I work here.</font>

102
00:07:02,905 --> 00:07:05,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Now I see.
-Huh?</font>

103
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:07,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was talking to Mitsuishi.</font>

104
00:07:07,905 --> 00:07:10,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He said since I was feeling down
about being turned down by you</font>

105
00:07:11,305 --> 00:07:14,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that I should come here.
He said I'd get over it for sure.</font>

106
00:07:16,205 --> 00:07:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What was he thinking?</font>

107
00:07:20,171 --> 00:07:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's so funny?</font>

108
00:07:22,605 --> 00:07:25,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think I'm getting over it now.</font>

109
00:07:27,805 --> 00:07:28,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not funny.</font>

110
00:07:28,872 --> 00:07:30,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's a friend of yours, Nao?</font>

111
00:07:30,972 --> 00:07:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Your boyfriend?</font>

112
00:07:34,039 --> 00:07:36,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hope to be. But she's turned me down.</font>

113
00:07:37,105 --> 00:07:38,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe, don't talk about that.</font>

114
00:07:38,605 --> 00:07:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow. You're unexpectedly popular.</font>

115
00:07:42,572 --> 00:07:44,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you mean, "unexpectedly"?</font>

116
00:07:48,505 --> 00:07:50,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here you go.
-Thank you.</font>

117
00:07:50,905 --> 00:07:52,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao.
-Yes?</font>

118
00:07:52,505 --> 00:07:53,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Before the end of the year,</font>

119
00:07:54,005 --> 00:07:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll get over the girls I've loved
this year.</font>

120
00:07:56,205 --> 00:07:58,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I'll start looking for new love
in the new year.</font>

121
00:07:58,472 --> 00:07:59,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good.</font>

122
00:07:59,572 --> 00:08:02,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think you need to be
a little more careful next year.</font>

123
00:08:03,205 --> 00:08:06,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know that's why they call you
the king of the love confession.</font>

124
00:08:06,905 --> 00:08:08,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But when I really like someone,</font>

125
00:08:08,605 --> 00:08:11,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just don't feel right
if I don't tell them.</font>

126
00:08:12,505 --> 00:08:15,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, that's right. I know how you feel.</font>

127
00:08:15,505 --> 00:08:17,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei, what are you talking about?</font>

128
00:08:17,405 --> 00:08:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm the type that says what I feel
when I like someone.</font>

129
00:08:20,105 --> 00:08:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep.</font>

130
00:08:21,705 --> 00:08:25,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When you don't do anything,
you regret it way longer</font>

131
00:08:25,205 --> 00:08:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">than when you do.</font>

132
00:08:28,705 --> 00:08:32,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can I call you "teacher"?
Ramen, please, teacher!</font>

133
00:08:32,872 --> 00:08:34,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-One order of ramen.
-Coming right up.</font>

134
00:08:36,505 --> 00:08:38,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">COFFEE SHOP</font>

135
00:08:38,105 --> 00:08:40,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You can go when you're done there.
-OK.</font>

136
00:08:41,305 --> 00:08:43,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hi, Uehara.
-Oh, hi.</font>

137
00:08:43,505 --> 00:08:44,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Uehara,</font>

138
00:08:44,572 --> 00:08:47,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">when are you going to tell me
your new address?</font>

139
00:08:47,672 --> 00:08:49,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll tell you
when you catch up to my age.</font>

140
00:08:49,705 --> 00:08:51,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's mean. I'll never catch up.</font>

141
00:08:52,105 --> 00:08:53,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanako. You've got studying to do.</font>

142
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:56,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not studying
until I get Uehara's address.</font>

143
00:08:56,605 --> 00:08:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Aw, jeez. Go ahead, you can leave.
-Yes, sir.</font>

144
00:08:59,405 --> 00:09:01,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Later.
-Hey, Uehara.</font>

145
00:09:01,939 --> 00:09:03,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">After work on New Year's Eve,</font>

146
00:09:03,505 --> 00:09:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">spend the New Year's countdown with us.</font>

147
00:09:05,305 --> 00:09:07,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Good bye.
-Thanks. Bye.</font>

148
00:09:10,872 --> 00:09:13,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Dad.
-What is it?</font>

149
00:09:13,805 --> 00:09:15,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I know you have it.
-What?</font>

150
00:09:15,772 --> 00:09:19,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara's new address.</font>

151
00:09:20,405 --> 00:09:22,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's personal information, you know.</font>

152
00:09:27,605 --> 00:09:29,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THE NEXT DAY</font>

153
00:09:33,705 --> 00:09:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so hungry.</font>

154
00:09:38,472 --> 00:09:39,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who could that be?</font>

155
00:09:43,972 --> 00:09:45,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

156
00:09:45,705 --> 00:09:46,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on in.</font>

157
00:09:46,705 --> 00:09:48,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Sorry for dropping in like this.
-It's OK.</font>

158
00:09:48,939 --> 00:09:50,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where's Uehara?</font>

159
00:09:50,305 --> 00:09:53,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I think he's working at the gas station.
-Excellent.</font>

160
00:09:53,405 --> 00:09:55,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When he's around,
he always pesters me to leave.</font>

161
00:09:58,105 --> 00:10:02,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I bought us some donuts.
-Really? Great!</font>

162
00:10:02,105 --> 00:10:05,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? You're still in your uniform?
Isn't it winter vacation now?</font>

163
00:10:08,205 --> 00:10:12,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">School hasn't gone well... So I...</font>

164
00:10:12,305 --> 00:10:13,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Remedial lessons, huh?</font>

165
00:10:16,105 --> 00:10:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I had to take them too.</font>

166
00:10:17,605 --> 00:10:20,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What? You?
-Uh-huh.</font>

167
00:10:20,805 --> 00:10:23,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Takuya, my husband,</font>

168
00:10:23,472 --> 00:10:27,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he always got good grades,
but mine were horrible.</font>

169
00:10:28,472 --> 00:10:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So his brains are inherited.</font>

170
00:10:31,572 --> 00:10:34,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here you go.
-Huh? New Year's gift money?</font>

171
00:10:35,005 --> 00:10:38,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll be traveling, so can you
give it to him on New Year's Day?</font>

