<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-OK, see you next year, Nao.
-Uh-huh.</font>

345
00:20:33,605 --> 00:20:36,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You two have a happy New Year.</font>

346
00:20:37,305 --> 00:20:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">DECEMBER 30</font>

347
00:20:40,305 --> 00:20:41,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What was this for?</font>

348
00:20:44,605 --> 00:20:45,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you up to?</font>

349
00:20:46,872 --> 00:20:49,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like you said,
I'm doing my New Year's cleaning.</font>

350
00:20:49,472 --> 00:20:52,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like they say, "Clean out this year's dirt
before the end of the year."</font>

351
00:20:52,705 --> 00:20:54,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Cleaning?
Looks more like you're making a mess.</font>

352
00:20:56,572 --> 00:20:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How rude! I'm getting rid of the clutter.</font>

353
00:20:59,705 --> 00:21:00,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Getting rid of clutter?</font>

354
00:21:00,672 --> 00:21:02,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You take out all of your things</font>

355
00:21:02,705 --> 00:21:05,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">then separate what you need
from what you don't.</font>

356
00:21:06,605 --> 00:21:09,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You just moved in. Is that all necessary?
I"m not sure if you're bright,</font>

357
00:21:09,505 --> 00:21:12,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">or if you're stupid.
I'm off to work.</font>

358
00:21:15,305 --> 00:21:17,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you... Oh!</font>

359
00:21:19,405 --> 00:21:23,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Tomorrow, I'm going to Daichi's place.
-You are?</font>

360
00:21:24,605 --> 00:21:28,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My mom told Daichi's mom about me</font>

361
00:21:28,305 --> 00:21:31,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so now I'm going to stay there
for New Year's Eve.</font>

362
00:21:32,105 --> 00:21:35,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see. You must be happy.</font>

363
00:21:36,072 --> 00:21:37,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides, I'll be out working.</font>

364
00:21:41,805 --> 00:21:42,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara has already promised</i></font>

365
00:21:42,872 --> 00:21:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to spend the New Year's countdown
with me.</font>

366
00:21:47,305 --> 00:21:48,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that's right.</font>

367
00:21:51,405 --> 00:21:53,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">NEW YEAR'S EVE</font>

368
00:21:55,472 --> 00:21:57,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's cold.</font>

369
00:22:03,605 --> 00:22:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Guess he's already at work.</font>

370
00:22:14,105 --> 00:22:15,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

371
00:22:18,872 --> 00:22:20,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dang, it's cold.</font>

372
00:22:32,939 --> 00:22:34,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

373
00:22:34,872 --> 00:22:36,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

374
00:22:37,305 --> 00:22:39,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The lights went out. Oh, no.</font>

375
00:22:40,839 --> 00:22:42,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where's the fuse box?</font>

376
00:22:51,605 --> 00:22:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, there it is.</font>

377
00:22:55,405 --> 00:22:56,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All right.</font>

378
00:22:58,805 --> 00:23:00,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think it's this one.</font>

379
00:23:01,705 --> 00:23:04,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. Are they back on?</font>

380
00:23:06,305 --> 00:23:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? How come they're not on?</font>

381
00:23:16,572 --> 00:23:17,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Manager, I'm here.</font>

382
00:23:18,039 --> 00:23:20,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Uehara. Is everything OK?</font>

383
00:23:21,505 --> 00:23:23,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-The blackout.</font>

384
00:23:23,105 --> 00:23:24,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't that where you live?</font>

385
00:23:24,972 --> 00:23:27,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I've been out since this morning.</font>

386
00:23:28,105 --> 00:23:30,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. I was worried about you.</font>

387
00:23:30,905 --> 00:23:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They said the trains had stopped too
because of the blackout.</font>

388
00:23:34,305 --> 00:23:36,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I'm glad you made it. That's good.</font>

389
00:23:36,772 --> 00:23:38,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's so cold.</font>

390
00:23:39,105 --> 00:23:41,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! That's cold!</font>

391
00:23:41,705 --> 00:23:44,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Why is there water here?</font>

392
00:23:44,905 --> 00:23:48,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Oh, no.</font>

393
00:23:50,405 --> 00:23:52,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oops!</font>

394
00:23:54,705 --> 00:23:57,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's soaking wet here.</font>

395
00:24:01,305 --> 00:24:03,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's all melted.</font>

396
00:24:07,505 --> 00:24:09,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">YOSHIKAWA NAO
CONNECTING</font>

397
00:24:14,105 --> 00:24:15,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Hello, Daichi?</i></font>

398
00:24:15,705 --> 00:24:19,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's me.
Sorry, but I don't think I can make it.</font>

399
00:24:20,305 --> 00:24:23,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I heard the trains have stopped.
You want me to come get you?</font>

400
00:24:23,105 --> 00:24:26,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's OK. The power is out here,</font>

401
00:24:26,505 --> 00:24:28,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so I think it's better
if I don't leave home.</font>

402
00:24:28,772 --> 00:24:30,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-<i>The power's out?
-Uh-huh.</i></font>

403
00:24:30,872 --> 00:24:34,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm sure it'll come back on again
pretty soon.</font>

404
00:24:35,305 --> 00:24:37,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>All right. I see.</i></font>

405
00:24:39,105 --> 00:24:42,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is he there? Uehara?</font>

406
00:24:44,305 --> 00:24:45,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

407
00:24:46,839 --> 00:24:49,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't think he's coming home today.</font>

408
00:24:51,105 --> 00:24:52,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

409
00:24:55,105 --> 00:24:58,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm perfectly fine.
I don't mind being home at all.</font>

410
00:24:59,405 --> 00:25:02,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I see. Bye.</font>

411
00:25:02,405 --> 00:25:06,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Daichi. Have a happy New Year.</font>

412
00:25:07,605 --> 00:25:08,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Have a happy New Year too.</font>

413
00:25:09,305 --> 00:25:10,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

414
00:25:20,839 --> 00:25:22,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It sure is cold.</font>

415
00:25:24,572 --> 00:25:25,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come to think of it,</font>

416
00:25:26,005 --> 00:25:28,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">the second-floor room will become vacant
next month.</font>

417
00:25:29,039 --> 00:25:31,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So it's true.</font>

418
00:25:31,105 --> 00:25:32,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, did Nanako say something?
-Yeah.</font>

419
00:25:32,905 --> 00:25:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I didn't think it was true.</font>

420
00:25:36,105 --> 00:25:38,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, usually I rent it for $700.</font>

421
00:25:39,105 --> 00:25:42,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But for you, I'll rent it for $500.
-Really?</font>

422
00:25:42,205 --> 00:25:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I can't pay for moving cost, though.</font>

423
00:25:45,505 --> 00:25:47,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're paying, what,
$700 to $800 now, right?</font>

424
00:25:48,072 --> 00:25:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

425
00:25:49,072 --> 00:25:52,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In the long run,
it's best to move to a cheaper place.</font>

426
00:25:53,305 --> 00:25:55,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I'll provide meals here too.</font>

427
00:25:56,872 --> 00:25:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But there is that pesky one here.</font>

428
00:26:04,105 --> 00:26:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>There has been a large scale blackout
in parts of the Tokyo area.</i></font>

429
00:26:08,672 --> 00:26:12,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>The power company says
that the power lines have been damaged.</i></font>

430
00:26:12,405 --> 00:26:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>However, they don't know what caused it.</i></font>

431
00:26:14,839 --> 00:26:18,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Without any idea when the power
will be back on, there are 3,500--</i></font>

432
00:26:26,205 --> 00:26:29,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Have a happy New Year!</font>

433
00:26:30,171 --> 00:26:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Best wishes for the New Year.</font>

434
00:26:32,505 --> 00:26:33,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you OK, Nao?</font>

435
00:26:34,105 --> 00:26:35,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's going to run out of power.</font>

436
00:26:36,072 --> 00:26:37,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">PLEASE CHARGE YOUR PHONE.
20% OF BATTERY REMAINING.</font>

437
00:26:39,605 --> 00:26:43,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I've got to turn it off
in case I need it for an emergency.</font>

438
00:26:43,605 --> 00:26:44,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">SHUTTING DOWN</font>

439
00:26:44,605 --> 00:26:45,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry everyone.</font>

440
00:26:51,205 --> 00:26:52,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's so cold.</font>

441
00:26:53,305 --> 00:26:55,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't know it could get so cold
with the power out.</font>

442
00:27:05,939 --> 00:27:09,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wish Uehara would come home.</font>

443
00:27:24,405 --> 00:27:25,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You may as well go home.</font>

444
00:27:26,039 --> 00:27:28,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But there might still be customers.</font>

445
00:27:29,705 --> 00:27:32,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll still pay you
for the hours you're scheduled for.</font>

446
00:27:32,672 --> 00:27:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Take it easy on New Year's Eve, at least.</font>

447
00:27:36,405 --> 00:27:39,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I appreciate it. Thank you.</font>

448
00:27:39,305 --> 00:27:42,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're closed tomorrow, New Year's Day.
Don't come in by mistake.</font>

449
00:27:43,305 --> 00:27:44,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

450
00:27:44,705 --> 00:27:47,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Manager,
thank you for all you've done this year.</font>

451
00:27:48,605 --> 00:27:49,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You have a happy New Year.</font>

452
00:27:49,872 --> 00:27:51,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will.</font>

453
00:28:03,472 --> 00:28:05,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>The number you have dialed
cannot be reached</i></font>

454
00:28:05,572 --> 00:28:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>because it has been switched off or--</i></font>

455
00:28:10,605 --> 00:28:13,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wish I could tell everyone,
"Happy New Year."</font>

456
00:28:25,205 --> 00:28:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">DAICHI, DAICHI, DAICHI,
MOM, MOM, MARINA</font>

457
00:28:27,205 --> 00:28:28,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">DAICHI, DAICHI,
UEHARA, DAICHI, DAICHI</font>

458
00:28:29,872 --> 00:28:30,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh.</font>

459
00:28:30,905 --> 00:28:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">UEHARA</font>

460
00:28:32,572 --> 00:28:34,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara called me.</font>

461
00:28:40,505 --> 00:28:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, please. Go through.</font>

462
00:28:50,605 --> 00:28:52,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-<i>Hello?
-Oh!</i></font>

463
00:28:52,872 --> 00:28:54,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello. Uehara?</font>

464
00:28:54,505 --> 00:28:55,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where are you now?</font>

465
00:28:56,072 --> 00:28:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I heard the power's out at home.</font>

466
00:28:58,472 --> 00:29:01,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh. It's really terrible...</font>

467
00:29:02,772 --> 00:29:04,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Are you OK?</font>

468
00:29:06,305 --> 00:29:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, I'm fine. Don't worry about me.</font>

469
00:29:11,572 --> 00:29:13,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Enjoy the New Year countdown.</font>

470
00:29:16,105 --> 00:29:17,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, bye.</font>

471
00:29:17,672 --> 00:29:18,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

472
00:29:19,205 --> 00:29:20,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara.</i></font>

473
00:29:20,705 --> 00:29:21,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah?</font>

474
00:29:24,905 --> 00:29:26,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Have a happy New Year.</font>

475
00:29:46,572 --> 00:29:48,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Have a happy New Year.</font>

476
00:30:00,705 --> 00:30:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ouch! Oh, oops.</font>

477
00:30:13,572 --> 00:30:15,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao? You here?</font>

478
00:30:21,005 --> 00:30:23,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, I knew she wouldn't be.</font>

479
00:30:24,572 --> 00:30:25,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm here.</font>

480
00:30:27,672 --> 00:30:29,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing here?</font>

481
00:30:30,305 --> 00:30:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't help it.</font>

482
00:30:34,205 --> 00:30:36,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Weren't you staying over somewhere?</font>

483
00:30:37,905 --> 00:30:40,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The trains aren't running.</font>

484
00:30:40,672 --> 00:30:43,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And the blackout caused problems
with the fridge.</font>

485
00:30:45,605 --> 00:30:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then why didn't you tell me?</font>

486
00:30:51,005 --> 00:30:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought it was odd your phone cut out
all of a sudden.</font>

487
00:30:55,405 --> 00:30:57,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I thought you were spending
the countdown at Nanako's.</font>

488
00:31:00,705 --> 00:31:03,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't want to bother you at work.</font>

489
00:31:05,072 --> 00:31:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What about you, Uehara?
-What about me?</font>

490
00:31:09,839 --> 00:31:11,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">From the start, I said...</font>

491
00:31:20,305 --> 00:31:21,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you to lean on me, right?</font>

492
00:31:25,905 --> 00:31:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

493
00:31:34,305 --> 00:31:37,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It sure is cold.
-Uh-huh.</font>

494
00:32:01,205 --> 00:32:03,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, it's lit.</font>

495
00:32:04,205 --> 00:32:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I got this candle
at my brother's wedding.</font>

496
00:32:16,405 --> 00:32:17,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's pretty.</font>

497
00:32:21,772 --> 00:32:24,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought about throwing it away.
Never expected it to be of use.</font>

498
00:32:25,305 --> 00:32:27,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's nice, warm and bright.</font>

499
00:32:29,605 --> 00:32:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I'm going to sleep here tonight.</font>

500
00:32:39,205 --> 00:32:40,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait, Uehara.</font>

501
00:32:41,939 --> 00:32:45,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What happened?</font>

502
00:32:47,405 --> 00:32:49,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did I do something stupid again?</font>

503
00:32:50,972 --> 00:32:52,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But what?</font>

504
00:32:59,805 --> 00:33:02,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If we're both in the same room,
that'll make it warmer.</font>

505
00:33:13,105 --> 00:33:14,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's so close.</font>

506
00:33:21,572 --> 00:33:23,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You changed?</font>

507
00:33:23,505 --> 00:33:26,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course. I'm going to bed, after all.</font>

508
00:33:27,105 --> 00:33:28,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. You're right.</font>

509
00:33:29,105 --> 00:33:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Man, it's cold.</font>

510
00:33:36,472 --> 00:33:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Don't you worry.
-What?</font>

511
00:33:38,939 --> 00:33:40,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't try anything with you.</font>

512
00:33:42,505 --> 00:33:44,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know that.</font>

513
00:33:44,305 --> 00:33:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of all people,</font>

514
00:33:46,405 --> 00:33:50,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know best just how unattractive
you think I am.</font>

515
00:33:51,305 --> 00:33:52,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you worry either.</font>

516
00:33:53,205 --> 00:33:56,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At the very least, I don't even expect you
to do anything like that.</font>

517
00:33:58,305 --> 00:33:59,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know that.</font>

518
00:34:14,205 --> 00:34:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you asleep, Uehara?</font>

519
00:34:18,605 --> 00:34:19,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep.</font>

520
00:34:24,072 --> 00:34:25,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

521
00:34:28,939 --> 00:34:31,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you leave home</font>

522
00:34:32,505 --> 00:34:34,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">because Yuri
and your brother got married?</font>

523
00:34:36,872 --> 00:34:38,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you asking that now?</font>

524
00:34:38,905 --> 00:34:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, you work so many jobs</font>

525
00:34:42,805 --> 00:34:47,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and suffer things you don't have to,
so you could leave home...</font>

526
00:34:50,472 --> 00:34:53,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just thought it must have taken
a lot of resolve to do that.</font>

527
00:34:57,405 --> 00:35:01,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I'm sorry.
That's none of my business, is it?</font>

528
00:35:03,972 --> 00:35:05,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let me ask you this.</font>

529
00:35:07,572 --> 00:35:11,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you loved someone who didn't love you
for eight years,</font>

530
00:35:13,505 --> 00:35:15,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">then that person got married
to someone else,</font>

531
00:35:18,405 --> 00:35:21,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">could you be around them
and still act normal?</font>

532
00:35:27,705 --> 00:35:29,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's why I did it.</font>

533
00:35:36,005 --> 00:35:38,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Won't you ever see your brother again?</font>

534
00:35:39,105 --> 00:35:42,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, I will. It's not like I hate him.</font>

535
00:35:45,039 --> 00:35:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You see...</font>

536
00:35:49,305 --> 00:35:51,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">the problem is my own.</font>

537
00:35:57,072 --> 00:36:01,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">However... I never plan on returning home.</font>

538
00:36:06,105 --> 00:36:07,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good night.</font>

539
00:36:11,305 --> 00:36:12,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good night.</font>

540
00:36:18,905 --> 00:36:20,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

541
00:36:21,005 --> 00:36:21,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

542
00:36:21,972 --> 00:36:25,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Is it past midnight?
-Way past.</font>

543
00:36:27,472 --> 00:36:30,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy New Year, Uehara.</font>

544
00:36:31,405 --> 00:36:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Best wishes in the new year.</font>

545
00:36:34,705 --> 00:36:36,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll try not to be too hard on you either.</font>

546
00:36:36,872 --> 00:36:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to sleep now.</font>

547
00:36:38,872 --> 00:36:40,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, me too.</font>

548
00:37:27,405 --> 00:37:30,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah, they came on. I'm so glad.</font>

549
00:37:31,572 --> 00:37:35,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I wonder if the trains are running.
-Why? Are you going somewhere?</font>

550
00:37:35,572 --> 00:37:38,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh. Daichi invited me to go
to a New Year's shrine visit together.</font>

551
00:37:38,205 --> 00:37:39,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you want to come too?</font>

552
00:37:39,905 --> 00:37:43,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's the New Year, and I think it's best
to do that kind of thing.</font>

553
00:37:43,305 --> 00:37:44,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're probably right.</font>

554
00:37:45,305 --> 00:37:47,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What? You'll come?
-You don't want me to?</font>

555
00:37:50,005 --> 00:37:50,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not at all.</font>

556
00:37:52,872 --> 00:37:55,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, not at all. Let's go!</font>

557
00:37:59,205 --> 00:38:00,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Darn it, Uehara.</i></font>

558
00:38:00,705 --> 00:38:02,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Your dithering has made us late.</i></font>

559
00:38:02,672 --> 00:38:04,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You've got no right to say that.
-Why?</font>

560
00:38:04,839 --> 00:38:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You only told me this morning.
-But you said you wanted to come.</font>

561
00:38:07,305 --> 00:38:08,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You should have told me yesterday.</font>

562
00:38:09,005 --> 00:38:10,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, give me a break.</font>

563
00:38:10,505 --> 00:38:11,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

564
00:38:13,105 --> 00:38:14,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Happy New Year.</font>

565
00:38:14,572 --> 00:38:17,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Best wishes in the new year.</font>

566
00:38:17,405 --> 00:38:18,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I brought Uehara along.</font>

567
00:38:19,672 --> 00:38:22,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hi.
-Hi.</font>

568
00:38:22,605 --> 00:38:24,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Was everything OK with the blackout?</font>

569
00:38:24,105 --> 00:38:27,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh, after Uehara came back home.</font>

570
00:38:27,772 --> 00:38:28,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

571
00:38:28,905 --> 00:38:31,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No big deal.
I just came to my own place.</font>

572
00:38:32,972 --> 00:38:35,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right.
You're acting like my parent, Daichi.</font>

573
00:38:36,305 --> 00:38:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I should have gone over myself.</font>

574
00:38:38,205 --> 00:38:41,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's all right.
Sorry for causing you to worry.</font>

575
00:39:22,705 --> 00:39:24,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was a long prayer.</font>

576
00:39:25,105 --> 00:39:27,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I probably overdid it for one dollar.</font>

577
00:39:30,171 --> 00:39:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

578
00:39:32,505 --> 00:39:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wanted to talk to you
about something the other day.</font>

579
00:39:35,305 --> 00:39:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

580
00:39:39,472 --> 00:39:41,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, I'll tell you later.</font>

581
00:39:43,672 --> 00:39:44,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

582
00:39:48,672 --> 00:39:50,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want a good luck charm.</font>

583
00:39:50,305 --> 00:39:52,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You should get one for safety
when traveling.</font>

584
00:39:52,839 --> 00:39:53,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good idea.</font>

585
00:39:58,505 --> 00:40:00,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, it's Mitsuishi.</font>

586
00:40:04,105 --> 00:40:04,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh my god!</font>

587
00:40:05,705 --> 00:40:06,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no!</font>

588
00:40:10,672 --> 00:40:14,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, I wish you all the best
in the new year, Nao.</font>

589
00:40:15,005 --> 00:40:16,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina, did you...</font>

590
00:40:19,205 --> 00:40:22,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're... going together now.</font>

591
00:40:24,105 --> 00:40:26,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Congratulations.</font>

592
00:40:26,772 --> 00:40:29,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you. This is thanks to you, Nao.</font>

593
00:40:29,805 --> 00:40:30,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that right?</font>

594
00:40:33,772 --> 00:40:36,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Why are you crying?</font>

595
00:40:37,005 --> 00:40:39,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Seriously?
-I'm just so happy.</font>

596
00:40:41,039 --> 00:40:44,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh gosh, here.
-Thank you.</font>

597
00:40:44,705 --> 00:40:49,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, you. Thank you so much.
-Congratulations.</font>

598
00:40:50,405 --> 00:40:53,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi getting that Great Fortune
was so perfect.</font>

599
00:40:53,472 --> 00:40:54,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who's Mitsuishi?</font>

600
00:40:55,205 --> 00:40:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What? You don't know?
-No.</font>

601
00:40:57,772 --> 00:41:00,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's been around since school started.</font>

602
00:41:00,905 --> 00:41:02,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Crap.</font>

603
00:41:04,072 --> 00:41:05,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Crap.</font>

604
00:41:16,505 --> 00:41:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Make yourselves at home.</font>

605
00:41:24,605 --> 00:41:26,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You're so mean, Uehara.</i></font>

606
00:41:26,905 --> 00:41:27,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

607
00:41:27,839 --> 00:41:29,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're supposed to
do the New Years count down together.</font>

608
00:41:30,005 --> 00:41:32,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You decided on that by yourself.</font>

609
00:41:33,505 --> 00:41:35,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't stand this.</font>

610
00:41:35,105 --> 00:41:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why? Why do you live with her?</font>

611
00:41:39,405 --> 00:41:43,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've known you so much longer than her.</font>

612
00:41:43,672 --> 00:41:48,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I love you so much more than her.</font>

613
00:41:50,171 --> 00:41:52,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Move over to our place, Uehara.</font>

614
00:41:52,305 --> 00:41:54,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>The second-floor room is only $500.</i></font>

615
00:41:54,705 --> 00:41:58,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>It'll be cheaper than this place
and easier to work there, right?</i></font>

616
00:41:59,805 --> 00:42:01,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your dad already told me that.</font>

617
00:42:01,872 --> 00:42:02,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then--</font>

618
00:42:02,872 --> 00:42:03,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I turned him down.</font>

619
00:42:07,072 --> 00:42:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Why?</i></font>

620
00:42:08,305 --> 00:42:11,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'm still in high school
and renting a new place isn't easy.</i></font>

621
00:42:11,605 --> 00:42:13,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sure Dad will do something
to make it easier--</font>

622
00:42:13,705 --> 00:42:15,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides...</font>

623
00:42:17,472 --> 00:42:19,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I enjoy living here.</font>

624
00:42:19,472 --> 00:42:21,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I have no intention of moving.</i></font>

625
00:42:25,305 --> 00:42:28,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>All right, now that you know how I feel,
get home and study for entrance exams.</i></font>

626
00:42:56,305 --> 00:42:57,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

627
00:43:00,705 --> 00:43:03,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm going to make dinner. You want some?
-Uhm...</font>

628
00:43:05,205 --> 00:43:07,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know you haven't realized this,
so I'm going to tell you.</font>

629
00:44:42,205 --> 00:44:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS IS A FICTIONAL DRAMA.</font>
